{"type":"answer","id":38405,"parentType":"question","parentId":6815,"uid":9688,"contents":"第二任期还没选上你就开始问能不能延长任期是不是有点钦点的意思（笑）<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://assets.pewresearch.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/12/2015/02/FT_16.01.06_presApproval.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://assets.pewresearch.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/12/2015/02/FT_16.01.06_presApproval.png\" alt=\"https://assets.pewresearch.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/12/2015/02/FT_16.01.06_presApproval.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n总的来说，美国总统大部分都是在第二任期开始支持度大幅度下降的，因为第一任期就到底的根本撑不到第二任期<br>\n<br>\n能够保持支持度甚至反升的差不多就克林顿一个。<br>\n<br>\n所以特朗普真能撑两个任期的话，大家也会习惯了他的好政策并且开始质疑他政策带来的问题。","date":"2019-08-16","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}